{"tid":1404775,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重新上路］我地唔需要指責 只需要檢討","createTime":"2019-08-04T06:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T21:57:13.000Z","uid":125542,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c37301b6b00c9d6a91fc7000a4b02c4a3a3bd4c8","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"尋晚再一次有好多前線手足被捕，同時亦都有好多冷氣軍師係度屌前線蠢，唔識走。覺得前線已經冇能力判斷成條戰線既方向，開始質疑大家留黎做咩？守黎做咩？<br />\n<br />\n我想講，你地雖然冇講錯，但係你地唔講其實前線都明，因為件事已經發生咗。唔通宜家前線仲會覺得守住條線係好有用？守住條線最後比人拉咗係正確？既然大家都明點解仲需要由你地呢班冷氣軍師係度開post屌，你估下個個都開呢啲指責post，結果係點？<br />\n<br />\n如果你地班冷氣軍師覺得仲係唔順氣，覺得班前線打擊左大家嘅士氣。我想同你地講，如果你上過前線，你會知道消息係極唔流通！好多消息會飛黎飛去但你又分唔到真假。更何況今次係有機會比班黑警混入左我地度放假消息要留要守。而你唔係諗辦法點去防，係喺度屌尻班前線，淨係睇表面。你同啲藍絲廢老屌尻後生仔搞亂而唔指向政府有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要既係諒解！要進步！要分析！永遠革命都係會犯錯架啦！唔係咁就比班黑警一下打沉呀？<br />\n<br />\n經過咁多次而得出既分析<br />\n中後排裝備一定會不足，所以遇到煙就會後退或者散開，架空前線既機會就大大增加。<br />\n而前線手足既心理質素亦都好難突破到唔怕被捕呢個關口，所以只有防暴推進既時候先可以有隊形咁後退甚至調番轉推前，原因係防暴需要成隊人連成一陣線，要一個扣一個，所以機動力低。示威者可以因應佢地既走位而做相應準備。但係遇到速龍大家都知有機會比人拉，所以就會亂！最後都係比人拉！<br />\n有其他手足都分析過點樣列陣對抗啲速龍，但係短時間內好難會訓練到一隊前線唔怕比人拉既心態。即使做到，我地主要都只係可以防，因為攻擊力點都會低過對方。可能你話我地既優勢係人多，但係如果雙方都列左陣，硬碰硬，我地都會比條街規限左我地人數嘅優勢。而我哋人數嘅優勢只會喺最前線俾人打低咗之後先發揮到果種源源不絕既效果，但係就會犧牲得太多，同埋越後裝備越少，所以都係比較難發揮，只可以喺無可奈何既情況下用。<br />\n<br />\n再分析埋黑警。就好似我上面講咁，我地心理質素仲味足夠。想像下就算唔圍捕，只係用速龍不斷捉人，當一次捉20個。捉10次呢？20次呢？我地未有呢個本錢住。<br />\n<br />\n所以喺呢個情況下，就要真正be water。我地要打好個基礎思想就係盡量唔好硬碰，即使下次有狗扮示威者，我地都要清楚形勢先，再架空番班卧底。<br />\n而另外，be water亦唔一定每一次都可以全身而退！所以前中後線都要盡量有哂裝備！因為你冇裝備，唔單止累自己，仲有機會累埋救你果個。我地全部人就會係因為少左一部分裝備而連累一大部分人。<br />\n<br />\n而最後亦都係我認為最重要既野，就係要理解自己每一次出去所做既野個目的同個期望既成果係咩？<br />\n遊行固然之係想make noise，想更加多人知道我地既初衷，加入我地既陣線去對抗呢個政府。<br />\n而我地同班狗對峙，可能就係想喺每一次當中揭發更多佢地濫權，罔顧法治既行為。但係經過左咁多次，班狗基本上已經差唔多樣樣都做齊哂，再上就已經係實彈。若果唔上到實彈的話，其實對峙個效果同期望已經發揮到最大，已經揭露晒黑警嘅所作所為，亦都深入哂喺市民既心中。而當大家都明白呢個位的話，明白到再對峙都好難有更大嘅效果，就會嘗試其他更好既方法，就係真正既be water！<br />\n<br />\n最後，就算大家經歷左啲咩，都要記住大家係喺同一隻船上面，先可以走到今日。<br />\n<br />\n緊記！<br />\n不分化，不割蓆，不流血，不被捕！<br />\n真正be water <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n8月5日  罷工，罷課，罷市。"},{"pid":"3ae9237542c096dfb558d488c0d2b9ee8335e33d","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"too long but please read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cf401a0bbf25c9d11f4c87085190b6b88c31ce","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"大家可以講 可以勸<br />\n但絕對唔可以屌同路人<br />\n無論和理非屌勇武 或 勇武屌和理非<br />\n大家坐埋同一條船 冇理由條船未到岸就自己整爛架船先"},{"pid":"33afa841992403ae4b6b382fa0e61bf5fbb23b15","tid":1404775,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n反省係好緊要"},{"pid":"a3a2e2723188878b796fe2ff39f5abce11fdc956","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望今晚唔會見到互屌Post！"},{"pid":"3d8378e05f8f798991b2649951143d4419925988","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"可以犯錯 但唔可以自亂陣腳<br />\n班狗都不斷犯錯 但佢地夠仆街唔理法紀先唔會亂<br />\n你估下如果佢地無理扑濕一個人就比人停職 佢地仲唔亂撚到仆街咩？<br />\n所以我地要團結！Fight as a team"},{"pid":"0c82bf3add9b15f9d7396a8681d0960e0ca9df0b","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"幫手推比多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"4d996d5d66543e0fdd53424983c022b354c04d48","tid":1404775,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家帶埋手足一齊升lv好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b55850c44aba062936b0a05a0cceb16c10a4339e","tid":1404775,"uid":69934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"幫推！ 係時候要多方面行動！ 我覺得以下巴絲個方案可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冷氣好貴，為咗支持環保8/8 7PM我去海港城涼冷氣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Weekday 升級支援方案 『和理非』都可輕鬆參與！（續）</strong></span><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403152</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f08a81fff6e3b660130e520781101f18432c1cc","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"各位手足兄弟<br />\n我地裝備可以升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">思想</span>都要升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場抗爭未完"},{"pid":"7c55378e29d0d0a2339a5c5d5efc0e720062b751","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad3f75875db15c2188dddb5ae4569f8729d4ea08","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:52:43.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef53ae104f2804cc7a2f00f8162f18b9e0ae53c6","tid":1404775,"uid":284139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:04:25.000Z","msg":"中後排要什麼裝備? <br />\n<br />\n如果不太高級, 會易買和數量多啲, 留多啲人"},{"pid":"6dce6359fdd1cf7c7dc2e880b7cc1936cbf6995b","tid":1404775,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:17:04.000Z","msg":"好多人話前線留係不理智<br />\n咁幾時留先算理智？<br />\n如果次次都佔完散 行完散<br />\n個政府根本就理鳩得你<br />\n前線尋晚講左句「兩個月啦，仲要等幾耐呀？」<br />\n到底點升級先逼到政府出黎？"},{"pid":"6ee7b61c2ba5564b704ae47eafa9d3fb78f0e172","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef53ae104f2804cc7a2f00f8162f18b9e0ae53c6","tid":1404775,"uid":284139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:04:25.000Z","msg":"中後排要什麼裝備? <br />\n<br />\n如果不太高級, 會易買和數量多啲, 留多啲人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"泳鏡、頭盔、豬咀（儘可能係）<br />\n冇呢幾樣一放煙陣型即散"},{"pid":"b64c675aee4960bb6f660def8f9e96fbe2d64523","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dce6359fdd1cf7c7dc2e880b7cc1936cbf6995b","tid":1404775,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:17:04.000Z","msg":"好多人話前線留係不理智<br />\n咁幾時留先算理智？<br />\n如果次次都佔完散 行完散<br />\n個政府根本就理鳩得你<br />\n前線尋晚講左句「兩個月啦，仲要等幾耐呀？」<br />\n到底點升級先逼到政府出黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:45:08.000Z","msg":"咁就要睇下留 係留幾耐？留到俾速龍捉先走？<br />\n我覺得留只係可以留到防暴全部上哂裝準備推果時就要散 因為每次出去既大部分目標已經完成，再留同啲狗對峙雖然可以再將士氣推上去，但有手足比人告暴動呢個代價太大，士氣會開始散。<br />\n每次大量防暴推，仲未包圍果時散，令到班狗覺得次次都捉唔到人，就可以大大力打擊佢地士氣。<br />\n我都知已經兩個月喇，但點即止先可以最有效咁攻擊呢個政府。大家要記得，我地面對緊既係共產黨，真係可以留守喺果度打狗就可以打贏？<br />\n但我地仲可以做咩？只有繼續不合作運動 make noise 繼續遊撃打擊班狗士氣 先係又有效又唔損兵既方法"},{"pid":"0de0aacf03d6765915137b96acbb1a7373ea6552","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:49:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"875af63ad20aeb141c56e9e3ae9eaba0f9b6680f","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b83dde5e30cacb0dccac850bf32cfb5bc2dde5d0","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:19:14.000Z","msg":"希望多D人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78f05303ae21950e6a06e8300f9fd14225d9c49","tid":1404775,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class